\section{General information}
 Keep record of different categories (books , journals , newspapers and  magazines ).
easy way to add new books .
Provide full information about every single book.
Different  criteria for searching book. (by title, author , subject , unique bar code).
Note panel to keep everyone updated .
Easy to log in and sign up.
Track the number of book available for one specific book.
Book reservation  in advance.

\section{TOP USE CASES}
 Add , Remove , Edit Books & information.
Search by different catalogs.
Register new account or delete old .
Borrow / Reserve / Renew / Return a book.
\newline
\section{main actors}
\newline 
 Person responsible for modifying books , items , users , check issued , reserved books record. 
Different users for search by different categories , booking , reserved and return books.
System for sending notifications about overdue books , canceled and new updates.
